Title: Bye-Bye Everyone! This Is the Only Way to Save the Earth
Writer: Aya Matsui, Hiroshi Toda, Akira Toriyama
Actors: Masako Nozawa, Mayumi Tanaka, Ryô Horikawa
Plot: As a desperate Cell prepares to self-destruct in an attempt to destroy the Earth along with him, Goku devises a last second plan to save everyone.
